data.description: Quality all brick home. This home boasts of gorgeous tray ceilings and crown molding throughout. New carpet and paint is featured. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space with a pantry and breakfast nook for those quick family meals. The primary bedroom is oversized with a walk-in closet. The primary bathroom has him and her double sinks with a large garden tub for those relaxing days after work and a separate  standup shower. This home sits on an oversized corner lot with a privacy fence and storage building as well. The two car garage has a newly installed garage door opener. Conveniently located 8.8 miles to the famous Buc-ee's and only 2.3 miles to the Historic Boone Tavern. I-75, shopping, dining, parks and schools are also close by. Don't miss this stunning property. Schedule a showing today!
